title: Strangest of Strangers (CRE108)
description:
A Classic RISK! episode from our first two years! In our eighth episode, stories recorded live at our October 28, 2009 show at Joe’s Pub by Moth host Ophira Eisenberg, 30 Rock’s Keith Powell, actor Mather Zickel, This American Life favorite Starlee Kine, and The Borowitz Report’s Andy Borowitz.

Support RISK! on Patreon at Patreon.com/RISK

author: Kevin@RISK-show.com (Keith Powell, Mather Zickel, Starlee Kine, Andy Borowitz, Impala, Stucky and Murray, Peter Salett, Jesse Krakow, Ophira Eisenberg, Kevin Allison)
